Package oracle.apps.fnd.applseed.config.ui.wiz

This package contains classes that support the UI wizard for Seed Data Configuration.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
SDContainerPanel Class assists in Seed Data Configuration.
SDCustomizationPanel Panel captures SQL fragment by View Object that will be used in custom customization checks on Seed Data Rows.
SDDriverPanel Class assists in Seed Data Configuration.
SDHandlerPanel Wizard Panel that will capture the SQL Handlers for Seed Data View Objects.
SDSummaryPanel Class assists in Seed Data Configuration.
SDSurrogatePanel Class provides the UI and the logic to handle Seed data configuration surrogate attribute requirements.
SDTreePanel Abstract class contains code to manage View Object tree that is dependent on the model panel tree.
SDWizard Wizard Class assists in the construction of Seed Data Configuration Application Modules.
SeedConfiguration Utility class consisting of static methods to handle configuration wizard tasks.
